trans-unit.source: FrameworkElementAdapters is used by [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-wpf-md.md)] add-ins to convert between a <xref href="System.Windows.FrameworkElement"></xref> and an <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.INativeHandleContract"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: FrameworkElementAdapters brukes av [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-wpf-md.md)] tillegg til å konvertere mellom en <xref href="System.Windows.FrameworkElement"> </xref> og en <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.INativeHandleContract"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-wpf-md.md)] extends the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winfx](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] add-in model to allow [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uisharpplural-md.md)] to be passed between host applications and add-ins.
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-wpf-md.md)]utvider den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winfx](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] modellen-tilleggsprogram for å tillate [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uisharpplural-md.md)] som skal sendes mellom vertsprogrammer og -tillegg.

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] requires that the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uisharpplural-md.md)] that are passed either directly or indirectly derive from <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement>.
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]krever at den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uisharpplural-md.md)] som er sendt enten direkte eller indirekte avledes fra <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement>.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement>

trans-unit.source: However, add-ins and host applications are typically run in separate application domains and are, consequently, separated by an isolation boundary.
trans-unit.target: Imidlertid-tillegg og et vertsnavn programmer vanligvis kjøres i egen programdomener og kan derfor, atskilt med et isolasjon grense.

trans-unit.source: For this reason, the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winfx](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winfx-md.md)] add-in model requires the types that are passed across the isolation boundary to be remotable.
trans-unit.target: På grunn av [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winfx](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winfx-md.md)] tillegget modellen krever typene som er sendt på tvers av grenselinjen utvalg ikke kan fjernstyres.

trans-unit.source: A remotable type conforms to one of the following: - Implements the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ISerializable> interface.
trans-unit.target: Typen kan fjernstyres samsvarer med en av følgende:-implementerer den <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ISerializable>grensesnittet.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ISerializable>

trans-unit.source: - Has the <xref:System.SerializableAttribute> attribute applied.
trans-unit.target: -Har den <xref:System.SerializableAttribute>attributtet brukes.</xref:System.SerializableAttribute>

trans-unit.source: - Derives from the <xref:System.MarshalByRefObject> class.
trans-unit.target: – Er avledet fra <xref:System.MarshalByRefObject>klassen.</xref:System.MarshalByRefObject>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement> is not remotable and must be converted to a remotable type before it is passed across the isolation boundary between an add-in and a host application.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement>er ikke kan fjernstyres og må konverteres til typen kan fjernstyres før den sendes på tvers av grenselinjen isolasjon mellom et tillegg og et vertsnavn-program.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement>

trans-unit.source: For this purpose, you need to call the static <xref:System.AddIn.Pipeline.FrameworkElementAdapters.ViewToContractAdapter%2A> method to convert the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement> to an instance of the remotable <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.INativeHandleContract>.
trans-unit.target: Du vil kalle statisk <xref:System.AddIn.Pipeline.FrameworkElementAdapters.ViewToContractAdapter%2A>til å konvertere den <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement>til en forekomst av kan fjernstyres <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.INativeHandleContract>.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.INativeHandleContract> </xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement> </xref:System.AddIn.Pipeline.FrameworkElementAdapters.ViewToContractAdapter%2A> for dette formålet

trans-unit.source: Once the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.INativeHandleContract> is passed across the isolation boundary, it must be converted to a type that can be displayed by the host application or the add-in.
trans-unit.target: Når den <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.INativeHandleContract>sendes på tvers av grenselinjen isolation må den konverteres til en type som kan vises av vertsprogram eller tilleggsprogrammet.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.INativeHandleContract>

trans-unit.source: In this case, the static <xref:System.AddIn.Pipeline.FrameworkElementAdapters.ContractToViewAdapter%2A> method is called to convert an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.INativeHandleContract> to a <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement>.
trans-unit.target: I dette tilfellet den statiske <xref:System.AddIn.Pipeline.FrameworkElementAdapters.ContractToViewAdapter%2A>metoden kalles for å konvertere en <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.INativeHandleContract>til <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement>.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement> </xref:System.AddIn.Contract.INativeHandleContract> </xref:System.AddIn.Pipeline.FrameworkElementAdapters.ContractToViewAdapter%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more detailed exposition of [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] add-ins, see [WPF Add-Ins Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For mer detaljert exposition for [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] tillegg, se [WPF-tillegg oversikt over](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Returns a <xref href="System.Windows.FrameworkElement"></xref> that has been converted from an <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.INativeHandleContract"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en <xref href="System.Windows.FrameworkElement"> </xref> som er konvertert fra en <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.INativeHandleContract"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.INativeHandleContract"></xref> that was passed across the isolation boundary between the host application and the add-in.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.INativeHandleContract"> </xref> som ble sendt i isolasjon grense mellom vertsprogram og tilleggsprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.FrameworkElement"></xref> that will be displayed from either the host application or add-in, depending on the direction in which the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] is passed between the two.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Windows.FrameworkElement"> </xref> som vises fra enten vertsprogram- eller tillegget, avhengig av hvilken retning den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] sendes mellom to.

trans-unit.source: Returns an <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.INativeHandleContract"></xref> that has been converted from a <xref href="System.Windows.FrameworkElement"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.INativeHandleContract"> </xref> som er konvertert fra en <xref href="System.Windows.FrameworkElement"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.FrameworkElement"></xref> to be passed across the isolation boundary between the host application and the add-in.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.FrameworkElement"> </xref> som skal sendes på tvers av grenselinjen isolasjon mellom vertsprogram og tilleggsprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.INativeHandleContract"></xref> that is passed from either the host application or the add-in, depending on the direction in which the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] is passed between the two.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.INativeHandleContract"> </xref> som er sendt fra vertsprogrammet eller tillegget, avhengig av hvilken retning den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] sendes mellom to.

trans-unit.source: root is not the root element of a tree of elements.
trans-unit.target: rooter ikke rotelementet av tre elementer.
